                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17900707-2-off8 t17900707-2-cd9"></join> last, one great coat, value 30 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17900707-2-victim52" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
